    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i know about the inr stuff but i feel like i'm overmedicated. if i start the 2mg dose tomorrow and just monitor how i feel, wouldn't i be able to tell if it's working? like if i don't get any sudden pains or bruising, it means the dose is fine, right? it feels safer to be on a lower dose than a high one anyway.",
